CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 17, 1956, pg. B11, reads: "'Bird Boys' of Pittsburgh getting their planes ready to wheel are, left to right, Jackie Butler, LuGene Bray, Milton Swan Jr., Sam Anderson and Leroy Randall Jr. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Jackie Butler, LuGene "Buddy" Bray, Milton Swan Jr., Leroy Randall Jr., and Sam Anderson seated in front, with radio-controlled model airplanes in K. Leroy Irvis' workshop
